    <item>
      <title>The beginning of the website</title>
      <link>https://shutowl.github.io/blog/beginning-of-website/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 19 Jul 2021 21:54:05 -0700</pubDate>
      
      <guid>https://shutowl.github.io/blog/beginning-of-website/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h5 id=&#34;posted-on-july-19-2021&#34;&gt;Posted on July 19, 2021&lt;/h5&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Today I felt like making a website. I mean, I had always meant to do it at one point,
but I had always put it off until today. &lt;a href=&#34;https://pages.github.com/&#34;&gt;Github Pages&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=&#34;https://gohugo.io/&#34;&gt;Hugo&lt;/a&gt; 
made it seem like it would be pretty easy to make one, but boy was I wrong. I spent pretty much all day trying to get it
to work, but at least it seems to work now, even if it does look pretty barebones right now.
I still gotta learn a bunch of stuff to make this blog look a little better, so I&amp;rsquo;ll work
on this website for now before diving into other things.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://shutowl.github.io/images/pochigga.png&#34; alt=&#34;maidpochita&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;I also need to figure out how to format images like this on these sites too lmao&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    
